verbose_text: It is found that the 4NBT and DMAB coexist, since the fingerprint vibrational peak of 4NBT at 1336 cm -1 for the -NO 2 stretching mode of 4NBT (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY in XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY) still exists, but decreases relative to the peak at 1575 cm -1 of benzene ring stretching vibration with the increase of the laser intensity.
